title: Fun in the sun with the Step2 Cascading Cove Sand & Water Table
description: Video review of the new Step2 Cascading Cove Sand & Water Table.

asset.author: Step2
asset.description:
Video review of the new Step2 Cascading Cove Sand & Water Table. For more information, please visit www.step2.com/p/Cascading-Cove-Sand-Water-Table

Step2 provided this dad with a sample to test as part of the Step2 Toy Tester program. For information on this program, please visit http://www.facebook.com/thestep2company

transcripts: Say hi. Hey guys I'm Ryan and this is Lincoln and we just want to thank Step2 for sending us this Cascading Cove Sand and Water Table for us to test out as part of their toy tester program.
